# Local-only. For production use `wrangler secret put <NAME>` instead.
#
# Copy to .dev.vars (gitignored) and fill in real values. Wrangler dev reads
# .dev.vars; production reads from `wrangler secret put` registered secrets.
#
# Required for production interview path:
#   GEMINI_API_KEY=...                # Already registered via wrangler secret put
#
# SpatialReal spike (feat/spatialreal-spike branch only — do NOT register in main):
#   SPATIALREAL_APP_ID=...            # SpatialReal Studio → dashboard → App ID
#   SPATIALREAL_API_KEY=...           # SpatialReal Studio → dashboard → API Key
#   VITE_SPATIALREAL_AVATAR_ID=...    # SpatialReal Studio → public avatars → Avatar ID
#                                      # VITE_* prefix exposes to client (avatar IDs are
#                                      # not secret; only API_KEY/APP_ID stay server-side)
